<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3772364>
    dc:description "FIGURES 1A–1E. Male genitalia of Rhyacophila longicaudata n. sp. 1A, left lateral, with left inferior appendage omitted. 1B, dorsal. 1C, ventral. 1D, phallus, ventral. 1E, phallus, left lateral. IX = segment IX, Pre = preanal appendages, Api IX = apicodorsal lobe of segment IX, Ana = anal sclerites, Api B = apical band, Sag = sagittal appendage, Ter = tergal band, Pha = phallus, Bas Seg = basal segment of an inferior appendage (paired), Api Seg = apical segment of an inferior appendage (paired), Aed = aedeagus, Phal= phallotheca, End = endotheca." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3772364/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3772366>
    dc:description "FIGURES 2A–2C. Male genitalia of Rhyacophila aksornkoaei n. sp. 2A, left lateral, with left inferior appendage omitted. 2B, dorsal. 2C, ventral. Par = parameres, Dor = dorsal process of the phallic apparatus, Ven = ventral plate of the aedeagus." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3772366/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3772368>
    dc:description "FIGURES 3A–3D. Male genitalia of Rhyacophila limsakuli n. sp. 3A, left lateral, with left inferior appendage and phallus omitted. 3B, dorsal. 3C, ventral. 3D, phallus, left lateral. Ana = anal sclerites." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3772368/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3772370>
    dc:description "FIGURES 4A–4C. Male genitalia of Rhyacophila kengtungensis n. sp. 4A, left lateral, with left inferior appendage and phallus omitted. 4B, dorsal. 4C, phallus, left lateral. Pre = preanal appendages, Api IX = apicodorsal lobe of segment IX, Ana = anal sclerites." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3772370/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

